OL,3,CWhich firms are being investigated
OL,4,Cover online pricing practices?
OL,6,FThe competition watchdog has launched
OL,7,Finvestigations into eight firms over
OL,8,Fonline pricing practices, including
OL,9,Fticket sites and driving schools.
OL,11,FThe Competition and Markets Authority
OL,12,F(CMA) said it had reason to suspect
OL,13,Fthe businesses had infringed consumer
OL,14,Flaw in relation to their use of fees,
OL,15,Fuse of misleading time-limited offers
OL,16,For by automatically opting consumers
OL,17,Fin for optional charges.
