OL,6,FThey described the opening of
OL,7,Finvestigations as an "important
OL,8,Fmilestone" in ensuring they "do the
OL,9,Fright thing by their customers".
OL,11,FBut which businesses are being
OL,12,Finvestigated and why?
OL,14,FTicket resale site StubHub is under
OL,15,Finvestigation over its presentation of
OL,16,Fmandatory fees.
OL,18,FThe CMA is specifically looking into
OL,19,Fwhether these fees are included in the
OL,20,Ftotal price the consumer sees at the
OL,21,Fbeginning of the purchase process.
