OL,3,CWhich firms are being investigated
OL,4,Cover online pricing practices?
OL,6,FThe CMA said it was investigating
OL,7,FAutomobile Association Developments
OL,8,FLimited - which trades as the AA, the
OL,9,FAA Driving School, BSM and BSM Driving
OL,10,FSchool - over its presentation of
OL,11,Fmandatory fees.
OL,13,FA spokesman speaking on behalf of both
OL,14,Fdriving schools said: "We are
OL,15,Fcomfortable that the #3 booking fee
OL,16,Ffor lessons is already transparent and
OL,17,Fin line with the CMA's rules and are
OL,18,Fmore than happy to additionally notify
OL,19,Fcustomers earlier in the journey as
OL,20,Fwell, which we have already done."
