OL,3,CWhich firms are being investigated
OL,4,Cover online pricing practices?
OL,6,FGold's Gym is under investigation over
OL,7,Fits presentation of a one-off joining
OL,8,Ffee for its annual membership.
OL,10,FThe CMA is also looking into whether
OL,11,Fthe way the firm presents this fee
OL,12,Fbreaks the law ` specifically by
OL,13,Fintroducing it part way through the
OL,14,Fsign-up process and not including it
OL,15,Fin advertised membership costs.
OL,17,FThe CMA said it was investigating
OL,18,Fhomeware retailer Wayfair to determine
OL,19,Fwhether its time-limited sales ended
OL,20,Fwhen they said they would.
